Holotype ♀. 1. Habitus, lateral view. 2. Head, frontal view. 3. Lower half of head, frontal view. 4. Antenna. 5. Head and mesosoma, dorsal view. 6. Propodeum, dorsal view. 7. Forewing. 8. Hindwing. 9. Metasoma, dorsal view. 10. Last metasomal tergite.
</paragraph>
